            </div>
            <div class="font-medium text-[var(--accent)] mb-1">B.F.A Studio for Interrelated Media</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)] leading-relaxed">Graduated with honors. Focused on video editing, event coordination, electronics, and art history.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

